OL,3,CMy Community Series: Learning a more
OL,4,Cthan 100-year-old Madeiran dance
OL,6,FPeople in Jersey have been sharing the
OL,7,Fimportance of keeping one Maderian
OL,8,Ftradition alive.
OL,10,FThe Bailinho da Madeira which is more
OL,11,Fthan 100 years old, includes dancing,
OL,12,Fsinging and musical instruments.
OL,14,FThe history of the Madeiran people is
OL,15,Freflected in the dance and the music
OL,16,Fto recreate day-to-day life such as
OL,17,Ffarming.
