OL,3,CMy Community Series: Learning a more
OL,4,Cthan 100-year-old Madeiran dance
OL,6,FRicardo George Freitas Martins says:
OL,7,F"We started with the ambition of
OL,8,Ftrying to keep the tradition alive and
OL,9,Fto bring a bit of home to Jersey.
OL,11,F"We trained a lot of the youngest
OL,12,Fmembers to dance and sing so all could
OL,13,Fbe part of the tradition."
OL,15,FThe group meets at St Helier's Town
OL,16,FHall every Wednesday and performs at
OL,17,Fevents like the Portuguese Fair.
