OL,3,CMy Community Series: Learning a more
OL,4,Cthan 100-year-old Madeiran dance
OL,6,FRui Vieira, Groupo de Folclore
OL,7,FMadeirense says: "When you perform in
OL,8,Fpublic, the public tells you how happy
OL,9,Fthey are and how happy they are to
OL,10,Fsing traditional songs from back home."
OL,12,FDuring the dance, those taking part
OL,13,Fwear outfits that reflect daily life
OL,14,Fin Madeira.
OL,16,FRicardo says: "My outfit is the
OL,17,Fshepherd, it is the man who used to
OL,18,Fwork in the mountains."
