OL,3,CMy Community Series: Learning a more
OL,4,Cthan 100-year-old Madeiran dance
OL,6,FWith the children of the group adding:
OL,7,F"We have to wear our hair in a bun,
OL,8,Ftraditional boots and a skirt.
OL,10,F"It is quite heavy, to be honest, but
OL,11,FI feel confident with it."
OL,13,FCeleste Freitas describes how the
OL,14,Fdance makes her feel, she says: "It is
OL,15,Flike something you are born with, it
OL,16,Fis something inside of your heart.
