OL,3,CMy Community Series: Learning a more
OL,4,Cthan 100-year-old Madeiran dance
OL,6,F"When I saw it had started here I was
OL,7,Fso pleased because it is something we
OL,8,Fare doing for our country as well as
OL,9,Ffor Maderia, me it's really really
OL,10,Fspecial."
OL,12,FThe group were filmed and interviewed
OL,13,Fas part of ITV Channel's 'My Community
OL,14,FSeries' which celebrates the
OL,15,Fimportance of coming together - it can
OL,16,Fbe a cookery class, a sports session,
OL,17,Ffriends meeting up and much more.
